#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-13-reflection-free-jsckson-serializers.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Enabling reflection-free Jackson serializers by default"
msgstr "默认启用无反射的杰克逊序列化器"

#. type: YAML Front Matter: synopsis
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-13-reflection-free-jsckson-serializers.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "In 3.35, we are going to enable reflection-free Jackson serializers by default."
msgstr "在 3.35 中，我们将默认启用无反射的 Jackson 序列化器。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-13-reflection-free-jsckson-serializers.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Some time ago, we started experimenting on how to improve the efficiency of JSON serialization and deserialization offered by Jackson and extensively used in Quarkus applications. From a performance point of view, Jackson's main bottleneck is its heavy reliance on Java reflection to access or populate data objects at runtime. To address this issue, we developed a build-time metaprogramming approach that generates reflection-free serializers and deserializers for Jackson."
msgstr "前段时间，我们开始尝试如何提高 Jackson 提供的 JSON 序列化和反序列化的效率，该技术在 Quarkus 应用程序中得到了广泛应用。从性能角度来看，Jackson 的主要瓶颈在于它严重依赖 Java 反射来在运行时访问或填充数据对象。为解决这一问题，我们开发了一种构建时元编程方法，可为 Jackson 生成无反射的序列化器和反序列化器。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-13-reflection-free-jsckson-serializers.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "In https://quarkus.io/blog/quarkus-metaprogramming/[this article] we explained how we implemented this feature in Quarkus and the performance improvements it brings. Since then, we have been continuously working to enhance this feature, fix bugs, and improve compatibility with various Jackson features."
msgstr "在 link:https://quarkus.io/blog/quarkus-metaprogramming/[这篇文章] 中，我们介绍了如何在 Quarkus 中实现这一功能，以及它带来的性能改进。从那时起，我们一直在不断努力增强这一功能，修复错误，并改善与杰克逊各种功能的兼容性。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-13-reflection-free-jsckson-serializers.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Configuring reflection-free Jackson serialization"
msgstr "配置无反射的杰克逊序列化"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-13-reflection-free-jsckson-serializers.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Given the experimental nature of this feature, we initially made it opt-in. To enable reflection-free Jackson serializers and deserializers in your Quarkus application, it is necessary to add the following configuration to your `application.properties` file:"
msgstr "考虑到该功能的试验性质，我们最初将其设置为选择加入。要在 Quarkus 应用程序中启用无反射的 Jackson 序列化器和反序列化器，必须在 `应用程序的 .properties` 文件中添加以下配置："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-13-reflection-free-jsckson-serializers.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "In the past months an increasing number of users have tried this feature, taking advantage of the performance benefits it offers, but also helping us to discover bugs, edge cases, and compatibility issues with various Jackson features that we have addressed one by one. Overall, we have received positive feedback from the community, so we have decided to make the obvious next step."
msgstr "在过去的几个月中，越来越多的用户试用了这一功能，不仅享受到了它带来的性能优势，还帮助我们发现了错误、边缘情况以及与 Jackson 各项功能的兼容性问题，我们已逐一解决了这些问题。总的来说，我们收到了来自社区的积极反馈，因此我们决定迈出显而易见的下一步。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-13-reflection-free-jsckson-serializers.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Enabling by default in the Quarkus 3.35 release"
msgstr "在 Quarkus 3.35 版本中默认启用"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-13-reflection-free-jsckson-serializers.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "At the moment the entire Quarkus test suite is passing with this feature enabled, and we have addressed all compatibility issues reported by users so far. Therefore, we have decided to enable this feature by default in the next Quarkus 3.35 release."
msgstr "目前，在启用该功能后，整个 Quarkus 测试套件均已通过，而且我们已经解决了用户迄今为止报告的所有兼容性问题。因此，我们决定在下一个 Quarkus 3.35 版本中默认启用该功能。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-13-reflection-free-jsckson-serializers.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "In order to cover the broadest possible range of use cases, we invite you to test your applications with this feature enabled, possibly also measuring its impact on performances. If you encounter any issues or have feedback, please report them on our GitHub repository or reach out to us on the Quarkus community channels. This will help us to be more confident about the stability of this feature and ensure a smooth transition for all users."
msgstr "为了涵盖最广泛的使用案例，我们邀请您在启用该功能后测试您的应用程序，并在可能的情况下测量其对性能的影响。如果您遇到任何问题或有任何反馈，请在我们的 GitHub 存储库中报告，或通过 Quarkus 社区频道联系我们。这将帮助我们对该功能的稳定性更有信心，并确保所有用户都能顺利过渡。"
